# Number of entities in Wikidata with X amount of statements. By: User:Infrastruktur
# Even if this query seemingly has to do calculations on all the 100M+ items in the graph.
# what happens here is it uses two of Blazegraph's optimizations to finish in less than a second.
# Due to technical limitations this has to count any type of entity, not just items, but also lexemes and properties.
#defaultView:LineChart
select ?val ?count
with {
  select ?val (count(*) AS ?count)
  where { [] wikibase:statements ?val . }
  group by ?val  
} as %i
where {
  include %i
  filter (?val <= 60)
}
order by ?val

